result.name: Lamma Grill

reviews.text: Solid food. Good beer selection at a reasonable price. Great view so sit outside.  Food took a little longer than expected but I’m not complaining.
Great food and service,  air con a little too high where I was sat definitely will go back

Nice little bar with a fantastic view of the sunset. The veggie burger was pretty good, and the IPA on tap was really delicious. The staff were very friendly, and the music was suitable for the relaxed atmosphere. Great prices for the area, and a good selection of bar food. It's worth coming for the view alone.
Good food, good music, good value

Great burgers! Took about half an hour for our food to arrive so if you’re in a hurry for a ferry, just something to be mindful of. But it was delicious so I’d say it was worth the wait. Staff are really friendly.
